  (text "SENSING SUBSYSTEM\n\nFunction:\n- Current transformer signal conditioning\n- RTD temperature measurement\n- Voltage sensing (DC bus)\n- I2C isolation for display/sensors\n\nKey Components:\n- Current transformer + burden resistor\n- MAX31865 RTD-to-digital converter\n- ADUM1250 I2C isolator\n- Voltage divider for OVP\n\nInterfaces:\n- SPI: MAX31865 (temperature)\n- I2C: ADUM1250 (isolated bus)\n- Analog: CT output, voltage divider\n\nReference:\n- CT_SENSING_DESIGN.md\n- MAX31865_Documentation.md\n- ADUM1250_Documentation.md"
